{"tid":803271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己吃肉卻逼愛犬吃素　她辯「讓牠更快樂！」上節目被打臉","createTime":"2018-09-02T06:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T08:08:34.000Z","uid":32511,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"952b97e8defbd6850da370853b9481c6d656816b","tid":803271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:44:34.000Z","msg":"近日一名英國飼主表示，為了讓狗狗更快樂，因此她決定讓愛犬「吃素」，為了宣揚這個<br />\n理念，甚至還帶著狗寶貝讓節目。但沒想到製作單位在狗狗面前放了一碗肉和一碗菜後，<br />\n這隻狗看見有肉，立刻「見獵心喜」，想也不想地就選擇了肉，讓狗主人好尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一名英國婦女露西（Lucy Carrington）近日帶著飼養的哈士奇「風暴」<br />\n（Storm），登上了談話性節目《今天早上》（This Morning）。她在節目出表示，因為<br />\n天氣炎熱的緣故，風暴變得沒有食慾，甚至還對肉興致缺缺。<br />\n <br />\n露西接著又說，直到將風暴的飼料換成了特製的素食狗糧後，牠就恢復正常了。露西還指<br />\n出，「吃素讓風暴變得更活潑、更快樂！」不過當主持人問露西是否是素食主義者時，她<br />\n卻說自己並不吃素，讓在場的主持人和來賓都相當驚訝。<br />\n <br />\n製作單位為了測試風暴是不是「素食犬」，也特地為牠準備了兩碗飼料，一碗是菜而另碗<br />\n則是肉。但讓露西傻眼的是，風暴當場走向那碗肉，並且大快朵頤。被自己的愛犬打臉，<br />\n露西尷尬不已，但她也辯稱是因為天氣轉涼了，風暴恢復了對肉的食慾。<br />\n<br />\n節目播出後，露西也被不少網友批評是「虐待動物」，也有獸醫指出，狗本來就是雜食性<br />\n動物，不只吃菜，也會吃肉，只讓牠們吃肉，是剝奪牠們的自由；而露西也表示，她會開<br />\n始餵風暴肉食，「如果這是牠想要的，那我會去順應牠」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/02/1525067-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F1525067-XXL.jpg&h=d67027d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/02/1525066-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F1525066-XXL.jpg&h=4dd56bb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ba04164dda5d78de554d3e9e57f9d06434a4aff","tid":803271,"uid":54681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23912898e6abe58047cd63fe844126fffc327cf9","tid":803271,"uid":144064,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"食齋既鯊魚"},{"pid":"9a20b3ccbdeffebda8fa21268f6dfa1eb9fe3737","tid":803271,"uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"23912898e6abe58047cd63fe844126fffc327cf9","tid":803271,"uid":144064,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"食齋既鯊魚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"讓牠更快樂！"},{"pid":"49aaaec02c46b8e42f4564776d81d7ed2c31c76c","tid":803271,"uid":196145,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"最鍾意呢啲電視台 <br />\n<br />\n專登扮訪問 實質係想踢爆人地啲大話"},{"pid":"e09ff255930df98f863d7d418aa773546ad53d5c","tid":803271,"uid":180248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"哈士奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673abda320b3b6e80831102fc11b8a76a8199fc1","tid":803271,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"白左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b2e61d6e85a7d772395d112b6e39e612ebaa1a","tid":803271,"uid":29080,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"四大岸狗<br />\n素食撚<br />\n女權撚<br />\n環保撚<br />\n耶撚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8215d928db69e5430a5ffc920f78a0205a786304","tid":803271,"uid":30830,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"49aaaec02c46b8e42f4564776d81d7ed2c31c76c","tid":803271,"uid":196145,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"最鍾意呢啲電視台 <br />\n<br />\n專登扮訪問 實質係想踢爆人地啲大話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"食齋嘅狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass